name: Alan Wilson
tweet: At the very least, we must expect these companies to help give parents the ability to protect their children. READ MORE:  https://t.co/4Fxdqta9Vs

name: Alan Wilson
tweet: Enough is enough. Threats to kids seem always lurking online and these companies need to step up and take responsibility. As a parent and as the Attorney General, I see how TikTok and Snapchat harm our children.

name: Alan Wilson
tweet: Today, we took action by encouraging @TikTok and @Snapchat to do the right thing to help parents better protect their kids from online predators.

name: Alan Wilson
tweet: Today, I helped launched SAFE, Sexual Assault Forensic Excellence, designation to support sexual assault victims.   I recognize the importance of forensic exams in evidence collection. These exams help build a case against perpetrators.  https://t.co/ZBv6s7HSFY
